118
0:04:54.26,000 --> 0:04:56,000
of them all: major ampullate silk.

119
0:04:56.26,000 --> 0:04:58,000
This is the silk that's used to make the frame

120
0:04:58.26,000 --> 0:05:01,000
and radii of an orb web, and also

121
0:05:01.26,000 --> 0:05:04,000
