292
0:12:07.26,000 --> 0:12:1,000
but it's unexpected results like this that make

293
0:12:10.26,000 --> 0:12:14,000
bio-prospecting so exciting and worthwhile.

294
0:12:14.26,000 --> 0:12:16,000
It frees us from the constraints

295
0:12:16.26,000 --> 0:12:18,000
of our imagination.

296
0:12:18.26,000 --> 0:12:2,000
Now I'm going to mark on

297
0:12:20.26,000 --> 0:12:23,000
